{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 电气安全答题程序数据分析\n",
    "\n",
    "本notebook用于分析电气安全答题程序的运行数据。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置中文显示\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['SimHei', 'Microsoft YaHei']\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False\n",
    "\n",
    "# 读取数据\n",
    "df = pd.read_csv('output/quiz_stats.csv')\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 数据统计摘要\n",
    "print('=== 数据统计摘要 ===')\n",
    "print(f'题目总数: {len(df)}')\n",
    "print(f'平均正确率: {df[\"正确率\"].mean():.2f}%')\n",
    "print(f'最高正确率: {df[\"正确率\"].max():.2f}%')\n",
    "print(f'最低正确率: {df[\"正确率\"].min():.2f}%')\n",
    "print(f'总参与人数: {df[\"答对人数\"].sum() + df[\"答错人数\"].sum()}')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 按难度分组统计\n",
    "print('\\n=== 按难度分组统计 ===')\n",
    "difficulty_stats = df.groupby('难度')['正确率'].agg(['mean', 'count'])\n",
    "print(difficulty_stats)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 正确率分布图\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))\n",
    "sns.barplot(x='题目ID', y='正确率', data=df, palette='viridis')\n",
    "plt.title('各题目正确率分布')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('题目ID')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('正确率(%)')\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.grid(axis='y', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 按难度分组的正确率箱线图\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 5))\n",
    "sns.boxplot(x='难度', y='正确率', data=df, palette='Set2', order=['简单', '中等', '困难'])\n",
    "plt.title('不同难度题目正确率分布')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('难度')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('正确率(%)')\n",
    "plt.grid(axis='y', linestyle='--', alpha=0.7)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 难度分布饼图\n",
    "difficulty_counts = df['难度'].value_counts()\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\n",
    "plt.pie(difficulty_counts.values, labels=difficulty_counts.index, \n",
    "        autopct='%1.1f%%', startangle=90, colors=sns.color_palette('Set3'))\n",
    "plt.title('题目难度分布')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 发现的问题分析\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. 题目难度分布不均\n",
    "- 简单题目占比过高（46.7%）\n",
    "- 中等和困难题目比例偏低\n",
    "- 建议增加中等和困难题目的比例，使难度分布更均衡\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. 部分题目正确率偏低\n",
    "- 题目11正确率仅36%，可能题目过难或表述不清\n",
    "- 题目8正确率40%，需要检查题目质量\n",
    "- 建议对低正确率题目进行审查和优化\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. 答题数据收集建议\n",
    "- 当前数据缺少答题时间信息\n",
    "- 缺少用户答题路径追踪\n",
    "- 建议增加答题日志记录功能\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. 程序改进建议\n",
    "1. 添加答题时间统计功能\n",
    "2. 增加题目难度动态调整机制\n",
    "3. 添加答题历史记录\n",
    "4. 增加成绩排行榜功能"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 输出分析报告\n",
    "report = f\"\"\"\n",
    "========================================\n",
    "    电气安全答题程序数据分析报告\n",
    "========================================\n",
    "\n",
    "【基本统计】\n",
    f"题目总数: {len(df)} 道\n",
    f"平均正确率: {df['正确率'].mean():.2f}%\n",
    f"最高正确率: {df['正确率'].max():.2f}% (题目{df.loc[df['正确率'].idxmax(), '题目ID']})\n",
    f"最低正确率: {df['正确率'].min():.2f}% (题目{df.loc[df['正确率'].idxmin(), '题目ID']})\n",
    f"总参与人次: {df['答对人数'].sum() + df['答错人数'].sum()} 次\n",
    "\n",
    "【难度分布】\n",
    f"简单题目: {difficulty_counts.get('简单', 0)} 道 ({(difficulty_counts.get('简单', 0)/len(df)*100):.1f}%)\n",
    f"中等题目: {difficulty_counts.get('中等', 0)} 道 ({(difficulty_counts.get('中等', 0)/len(df)*100):.1f}%)\n",
    f"困难题目: {difficulty_counts.get('困难', 0)} 道 ({(difficulty_counts.get('困难', 0)/len(df)*100):.1f}%)\n",
    "\n",
    "【问题发现】\n",
    "1. 难度分布不均，简单题目占比过高\n",
    "2. 题目11正确率仅36%，需要审查\n",
    "3. 建议增加答题时间统计功能\n",
    "\n",
    "【改进建议】\n",
    "1. 增加中等和困难题目数量\n",
    "2. 优化低正确率题目\n",
    "3. 添加答题日志记录\n",
    "\n",
    "========================================\n",
    "报告生成时间: 2026-06-07\n",
    "========================================\n",
    "\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "print(report)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 保存报告\n",
    "with open('output/analysis_report.txt', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n",
    "    f.write(report)\n",
    "\n",
    "print('分析报告已保存到 output/analysis_report.txt')"
   ]
  }
 ],
